Ebanking 好似每日最多50次？"},{"pid":"cf85689f00038108f7aa71f7ebf0ef3b1230959d","tid":1824573,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"J果行係邊到？搵唔到"},{"pid":"67c221f0f210c824fd6c96fcbb4fe879a33593e9","tid":1824573,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"推，好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7c179b0c28e4cc224c49e6e792c56d8ee0707a","tid":1824573,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T23:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc412dd64ca907080469cbec7da70184157fa85","tid":1824573,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"邊個bank冇限制"},{"pid":"92a08f4fd6829207454339dabb942c53c3df1ebe","tid":1824573,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8ee6742cc158d6715ca61684eabfb8cac61963b","tid":1824573,"uid":66615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29658028cd15f4a0ef32a0d78e03e2bc0bde900f","tid":1824573,"uid":264915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"但稅單要6個星期交..<br />\nEBANKING 每日50次上限....每日不停做都交唔足稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇手足有方法呀？...我諗唔到.........."},{"pid":"93d5c56feda59431acd6151f1da90790e0cb61a6","tid":1824573,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01