/>\n<br />\nd) 碌落去底click繼續 (最好click 正中D, 無咁易走位)<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rhYMotB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrhYMotB.jpg&h=505af6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ne) 呢度再scroll down 一次, click 確認<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuPf1gp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyuPf1gp.png&h=5cb8add8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nf) 咁就比左一次, 成功爭取幫政府蝕$1.1<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Euv3qH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuv3qH7.png&h=c3d4f619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ng) 再scroll down, click 新交易<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zePS3uR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzePS3uR.jpg&h=8dee1e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nh) 咁就會番到第一頁, 你可以Ctrl + Q 或者click stop recording 停止錄影<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58gYY3x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58gYY3x.png&h=281d15cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ni) 之後就係最開心既攬炒時間! 大叫 &quot;我要攬炒!&quot; 之後，一野click落個play度<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWXmcoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWXmcoB.jpg&h=db9f7277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nj) 我要攬炒幾多次? 我希望攬炒到煲底見先停呀! (由於大約30秒左右一圈, 未到煲底相見果日之前可以set 住 150次試run一個鍾左右先)<br />\n <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4WmWQn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4WmWQn.png&h=7ebb9509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小提示:<br />\n1. 建議開fullscreen 之後先開始record, 開始左play之後unplug mouse, 會少D走位問題<br />\n2. 由於佢係錄低你既動作重播, 你click得慢佢就慢, 你click得快佢就快。建議每次轉頁果陣停一停等佢load，如果唔係甩一次就pay唔到落去。(恆生網站反應好快, 可以極速狂click唔使停, 但一日最多只能pay 50次) Citibank 就穩定地慢...<br />\n3. 有心機既手足可以edit 下D動作, 減少D 無需要既Delay位, D 無意義既mouse 移動都可以delete。咁個圈就可以行快D。<br />\n<br />\n我地提出呢個方法只係拋磚引玉，如果其他手足有其他攬炒交稅方法請隨便提出。有咩銀行試左得同唔得歡迎分享。<br />\n<br />\n請大家每日堅持抗爭，不分化不割蓆。記得記得不被捕不受傷，手足們記得我地要煲底見!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:25:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求巴絲解答，想問下去渣打開支票戶口<br />\n再叫佢地開全部$1支票或$0.1支票使唔使收費？<br />\n再過幾日cut戶口得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n另外郵寄但唔夠郵費會點？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"叫銀行開果d 好似叫本票.....65歲(或以上)廢老可以免手續費<br />\n<br />\n好似係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68e02825d3ea7d6fa6305904ef09b02fac0d662","tid":1824573,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"留名研究下"},{"pid":"33e3ea43053dafd45313c8e31cf6fc140f6de314","tid":1824573,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d1c8618dfd82e50da7686bf7171fb57201bb3e3e","tid":1824573,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:15:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b12fd07dda639f2a1ce978ba3710d21edafc7107","tid":1824573,"uid":224755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:31:34.000Z","msg":"有人話政府同銀行傾左一日淨係收一次手續費"},{"pid":"c7ca1ea8b94ea2d4572c5fd9d2a33978e8222d16","tid":1824573,"uid":66615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12fd07dda639f2a1ce978ba3710d21edafc7107","tid":1824573,"uid":224755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:31:34.000Z","msg":"有人話政府同銀行傾左一日淨係收一次手續費"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:55:47.000Z","msg":"請FC"},{"pid":"5d37d46b2353dc78240a7c0c3e759ae698b99b8e","tid":1824573,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67521c10f22f36f052e85face18bf1bc427ae800","tid":1824573,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smil